@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dazlsw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((0.22 + (v1 + 0.31 - tmp + 0.96)))
    v2 = v1
    v1 = v2
    v0 = v2
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.69 * v0 + 0.16) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.94)) / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.72) - tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
